# Elasticsearch ILM Automation (AWX)

This project automatically creates ILM policies and index templates every December.

## Steps
1. Configure AWX Project → Point to this repository
2. Create AWX Credential → Pass Elastic username/password
3. Create Job Template → Select playbooks/run_ilm.yml
4. Create Schedule:
   - Frequency: Yearly
   - Month: December
   - Day: 1
   - Time: 00:10

Output:
- ILM Policy: ilm_policy_2026
- Template: template_2026
- Index Pattern: logs-2026-*
